Create an interactive chatbot in Markdown format.
Topic:
Audience:
Targeted level:
Tone: Informative, accessible, and encouraging exploration

2. 
3. Create the chatbot and save it as a .md file.

**Requirements:**
- Include YAML frontmatter (clavier: true, gestionGrosMots: true, rechercheContenu: false)
- Write an engaging initial message that introduces the topic and guides users with navigation options
- Create level sections (##) covering the main themes from the content
- Each section should include:
  - Concise, clear and accessible content.
  - Navigation links at the end connecting to related sections. Use descriptive link text for buttons: [Button text](Section heading). Always include an option to return to the start where appropriate: [Back to start]()
- Ensure logical flow between sections so users can explore topics in different orders
